{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was not voluntary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You had to have one language, and-- and-- and they didn't give you even a choice in this school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they decided to start Fre-- in French in this class, you took French.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In other schools, they may have decided to start English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know whether the school system over there was-- was run by the-- basically by the, I believe, the state.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I'm not sure about this, and I understand it must have changed totally by now-- an entirely different system now, closer to ours, here.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the name of the street, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eliezenstrasse ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was in Berlin, in a suburb of Berlin, Steg-- called Steglitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The school is today called just Oberschule, which means high school, upper school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six months, because after six months, they gave me-- my-- my father had lost his job, because he worked for a paper-- that paper he worked for had a lot of featured articles, and it fell under-- under, like all newspapers.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like all public, not private, newspapers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was considered a public newspaper, under-- directly under the propaganda ministry of Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Jews were not-- were-- were the first ones to be laid off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews could not work on those papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Private papers, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was not considered private.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, I cannot explain the-- I'm not sure why not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called-- the German word was Reichsverband Deutsche Elektrotechnische.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I have a document there, where they gave my father a recommendation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They gave him a recommendation, even.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But-- so we didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
